data.value: SELECT A.SLIP_CODE SLIP_CODE , B.SLIP_NAME SLIP_NAME , A.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE , A.HANGMOG_NAME HANGMOG_NAME , A.HOSP_CODE HOSP_CODE , NVL(A.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') WONNAE_DRG_YN FROM OCS0142 C , OCS0102 B , OCS0103 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE AND ( ( :f_mode = '1' AND A.ORDER_GUBUN = :f_order_gubun ) OR ( :f_mode = '2' AND -- A.HANGMOG_NAME_INX LIKE '%'||:f_search_word||'%' ) A.HANGMOG_NAME_INX LIKE :f_search_word ) ) AND TO_DATE(:f_order_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND NVL(A.END_DATE, TO_DATE('99981231', 'YYYYMMDD')) AND ( ( A.ORDER_GUBUN IN ( 'B', 'C', 'D' ) AND NVL(A.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') LIKE :f_wonnae_drg_yn ) OR ( A.ORDER_GUBUN NOT IN ( 'B', 'C', 'D' ) ) ) AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.ORDER_GUBUN = A.ORDER_GUBUN AND C.INPUT_TAB = :f_input_tab AND ( ( C.MAIN_YN != 'Y' ) OR ( C.MAIN_YN = 'Y' AND A.IF_INPUT_CONTROL != 'P' ) ) AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.SLIP_CODE = A.SLIP_CODE ORDER BY A.SLIP_CODE, A.HANGMOG_NAME
